                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">All ages and all devices easy and intuitive to use. User manuals becoming something of the past.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 ml-md-auto mr-md-auto feature">
                    <%= image_tag("/front-assets/lock.svg", :alt => "Bitcoin", :class => "img") %>
                    <h4 class="title feature-title-color leading-sm">Cryptography</h4>
                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">Blockchain technology impossible to hack and without any third-party involvement.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 feature">
                    <%= image_tag("/front-assets/tv.svg", :alt => "Bitcoin", :class => "img") %>
                    <h4 class="title feature-title-color leading-sm">Whiteboard</h4>
                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">Use the Whiteboard for drawing all kinds of infographics or create a Kanban for the team.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row second-row">
                <div class="col-md-3 feature">
                    <%= image_tag("/front-assets/mike.svg", :alt => "Bitcoin", :class => "img") %>
                    <h4 class="title feature-title-color leading-sm">Polling</h4>
                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">Make your instant Poll in the Room you are chatting to your friends and colleagues.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 ml-md-auto mr-md-auto feature">
                    <%= image_tag("/front-assets/faces.svg", :alt => "Bitcoin", :class => "img") %>
                    <h4 class="title feature-title-color leading-sm">Face Filter</h4>
                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">Look your best with the Face enhancement AI-software of worldleader Banuba. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <%= image_tag("/front-assets/vaiyo-icon.svg", :alt => "Bitcoin", :class => "img") %>
                    <h4 class="title feature-title-color leading-sm">VAIYO Token</h4>
                    <p class="excerpt feature-excerpt-color">Monetize with VAIYO token, invest instead of buying. Get full functionality and VAIYO tokens. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="vaiyo-uses" class="bg-grey">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="row business-personal-use">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-4 leading-default">
                    <div class="title">
                        <h1 class="mb-0">Business, School and Personal use </h1>
                        <hr class="title-border m-0" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <p class="desc text-light-black">Recognize a good application when using  it everytime on all occasions on all your devices and everwhere you go.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="goto-link text-white text-center rounded-circle float-right mobile-hide"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 offset-lg-2">
                    <div class="business-icons">
                        <%= image_tag("/front-assets/business-icon.png", :alt => "Business Icon") %>
                    </div> 
                    <div class="goto-link text-white text-center rounded-circle float-right desktop-hide"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="app" class="bg-grey overflow-hidden">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 app-img">
                <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h1 class="title fw-600 leading-default mb-0">Transfer Crypto P2P in video call</h1>
                    <hr class="title-border m-0" />
                </div>
                <%= image_tag("/front-assets/app.png", :alt => "App", :class => "img") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 content">
                <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h1 class="title fw-600 leading-default mb-0">Transfer Crypto P2P in video call</h1>
                    <hr class="title-border m-0" />
                </div>
                <p class="desc text-light-black mb-0">Crypto Payments becoming more popular because of their low transfer fee and high speed, with no interference of any third-party.Soon you can do Crypto Payments in a videocall knowing for sure to who you are paying.</p>
                <div class="goto-link text-white text-center rounded-circle float-right"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="partners" class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="title-between-wrapper text-center">
            <h1 class="title fw-600 leading-default m-0">Our Partners</h1>
            <div class="border"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="partners-wrapper">
            <% if @partners %>
                <div class="row">
                    <% @partners.each do |partner| %>
                        <div class="col-md-2 partner-block">
                            <div class="partner">
                                <%= image_tag(partner.logo.url, :alt => partner.name, :class => "img partner-image") %>
                                <%= image_tag(partner.logo.url, :class => "partner-img-none d-none") %>
                                <%= image_tag(partner.replacement_logo.url, :alt => partner.name, :class => "img partner-replacement-image d-none") %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="roadmap" class="bg-grey">
        <div class="roadmap-wrapper container mx-auto">
            <div class="title-between-wrapper text-center">
                <h1 class="title fw-600 leading-default m-0">Road Map</h1>
                <div class="border"></div>
            </div>
            <table class="table roadmap-table">
                <tbody>
                    <% if @firstStepsMilestone %>
                        <% @firstStepsMilestone.each do |milestone| %>
                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="btn-blue text-white">Week <%= milestone.week %> <%= milestone.year %></div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="item"><%= milestone.milestone.html_safe %></td>

                                <% @milestones.each do |remainingMilestones| %>
                                    <% if (remainingMilestones.year == milestone.year && remainingMilestones.week == milestone.week) %>
                                        <td class="item"><%= remainingMilestones.milestone.html_safe %></td>
                                    <% end %>
                                <% end %>
                            </tr>
                        <% end %>
                    <% end %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="footer" class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3 column-1">
                <%= image_tag("/front-assets/logo.svg", :alt => "Vaiyo Logo") %>
                <p class="excerpt leading-default mb-0">Find Vaiyo on Social Media and start reading about us and communicating with us.</p>
                <ul class="social-media p-0 mb-0">
                    <li class="icon"><%= image_tag("/front-assets/google.svg", :alt => "Google") %></li>
                    <li class="icon ml-4"><%= image_tag("/front-assets/twitter.svg", :alt => "Twitter") %></li>
                    <li class="icon ml-4"><%= image_tag("/front-assets/linkedin.svg", :alt => "Linkedin") %></li>
                    <li class="icon ml-4"><%= image_tag("/front-assets/fb.svg", :alt => "Facebook") %></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 menu-wrapper column-2">
                <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h4 class="title mb-0 fw-700">Product</h4>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-1">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-1 rounded-circle">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-2 rounded-circle">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="menu p-0 mb-0">
                    <li class="menu-item">Landingpage</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Features</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Referral Program</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Pricing</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 menu-wrapper column-3">
                <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h4 class="title mb-0 fw-700">Services</h4>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-1 rounded-circle">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-2 rounded-circle">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="menu p-0 mb-0">
                    <li class="menu-item">
                        <%= link_to "Whitepaper", "https://vaiyo.io/media/Vaiyo-whitepaper.pdf", target: "_blank" %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Crypto Transfers</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Rooms</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-5">Wallet</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 menu-wrapper column-4">
                <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h4 class="title mb-0 fw-700">Company</h4>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-1 rounded-circle">
                        <hr class="dotted-border border-2 rounded-circle">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="menu p-0 mb-0">
                    <li class="menu-item">Team</li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-4">
                        <%= link_to "Term Of Use", "https://vaiyo.io/media/terms_of_use.pdf", target: "_blank" %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="menu-item mt-4">
                        <%= link_to "Acceptable Use Policy", "https://vaiyo.io/media/acceptable-use-policy.pdf", target: "_blank" %>
